<section class="model-section">
  <div class="model-container">
    <h2 class="model-heading">Our way is simple.</h2>
    <p class="model-subtext">
      Fast scheduling, no surprise bills, and the highest clinical standards — backed by real people who care.
    </p>

    <div class="model-grid">
      <!-- Traditional Way -->
      <div class="model-box model-dark">
        <h3>The Traditional Way</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><span class="icon">⚠️</span> Prices can range from $1,200 to $7,000 — even with insurance.</li>
          <li><span class="icon">⚠️</span> Low transparency. Surprise billing is common.</li>
          <li><span class="icon">⚠️</span> Outdated equipment at some centers.</li>
          <li><span class="icon">⚠️</span> Difficult to know who reads your scan.</li>
          <li><span class="icon">⚠️</span> No help matching you to the right center.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- USRad Way -->
      <div class="model-box model-light">
        <h3>The USRad Way</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><span class="icon">✅</span> Pricing starts under $400 — transparent and upfront.</li>
          <li><span class="icon">✅</span> No surprise bills. Know the cost before you book.</li>
          <li><span class="icon">✅</span> Only modern, accredited imaging centers.</li>
          <li><span class="icon">✅</span> Board-certified radiologists. No shortcuts.</li>
          <li><span class="icon">✅</span> SmartMatch™ matches you based on your scan and needs.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .model-section {
    background: #0e1b2a;
    color: white;
    padding: 6rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .model-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .model-heading {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #e6c378;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .model-subtext {
    color: #cbd5e1;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }
  .model-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .model-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }
  .model-box {
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }
  .model-dark {
    background-color: #1a2736;
  }
  .model-light {
    background-color: white;
    color: #0e1b2a;
    border: 1px solid #e6c37840;
  }
  .model-box h3 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .model-box ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .model-box li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .model-light li {
    color: #1e293b;
  }
  .icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
  }
</style>
